Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎一般的神父  亞當·佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃·諾伊修凡·舒坦因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及  其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在正在西美翁大樓內展開著激戰熱斗…

Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於沉不住氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一幫蠢貨們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站著等了好幾個小時的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰都會忍耐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼奠基活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們666邀請過來  卻是這個表現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幾個傢伙  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會闖進我們這間屋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能擺平他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎還沒得到新的肉體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會很快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗香  夏樹  結愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  璃琉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  本人原創的混合超必殺技  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特攻  熔岩-little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不稀罕你脫襪子的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以直接幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判決  死刑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了四天王之一的安路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  快治療大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點來吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呸  抹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塗上口水就Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治好就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重創到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娃  左天他醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我有些輕敵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.26,0:05:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你幹掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下你一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復意識了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  幸虧有迪斯克  夏娃  還有佈雷德他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也因為你自己很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  快瞧瞧看  在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被佈雷德打了個七零八落  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像垃圾  破抹布一樣慘兮兮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打倒了對方就損人家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此的話  至少把我最大的污點…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給抹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩那麼多力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  她的目標是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  庫魯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趁機保護山田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個…什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你睡覺的功夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就痊癒了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安路卡的拳頭怎麼會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是血脈相連的姐弟  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的內心深處是有弱點的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  我沒讓拳頭停住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是重力或是磁力的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不是…那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  退下吧  安路卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當·阿克萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜碎…我不再這麼稱呼你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓兩位四天王敗下陣來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要承認你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可算是出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡蹲的小少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許無禮  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是忘了  我是神這一事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷襲了我一下而已  別得意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  邀我們來這裡而你自己卻遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼害怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了  因為外面的人又吵了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓他們靜下來可並不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過放心吧  我擺平一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺平了的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把外面的人們怎麼樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我命令璃琉出動了少女部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女部隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:33.63,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀する乙女には　常識通じない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:33.63,Banner,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛中的少女　完全不合情理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉辦了一場少女部隊的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託大家拍拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪一下子就安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  真令人放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想去看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人別這樣  最終BOSS就在眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日所受的最大傷害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左天大人  請您走樓梯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是四天王耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  去瞧瞧那些老頭子們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.98,0:11:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家來捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫結愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結愛醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後～我是穗香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穗香醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在群眾當中查出了數個NEEDLESS擁有未被我們圖書館記載的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璃琉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我司西美翁大樓左翼頂層  瞭望台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這風景不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是舊東京
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們築巢的爆炸中心地  Black Spot
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是對你們而言的最後一道風景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒問過你的名字呢  神父
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德  今天是值得紀念的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.74,0:12:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我獲得新肉體的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個曾經屬於佈雷德的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態  憑什麼想霸佔我的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心臟那裡有機器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來不止是右眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個心臟和右眼的傷  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論動用多麼高超的醫療技術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或是何種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒法治癒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一旦得到了你的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能進化為完美的神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像無數科學家們曾經描繪的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初見他的時候  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:13:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是有人拿亞當計劃的遺產  造出了新的亞當
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那個右眼和心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了  他就是那個時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男的有些眼熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六根道·銀博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是左天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參與亞當計劃的科學家之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當計劃  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說那次爆炸的倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你之外還有別人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起初我也不相信自己的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向城裡的科學家們賣乖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把自己變成神的克隆體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種人渣  立即給我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴風雨細絲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dean·Drive-F·H  +
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高溫爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然一次都打不著他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吞噬了迄今為止見過的所有NEEDLESS  或讓他們淪為仆下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的能力都集聚於我一身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  你此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在與我認識的所有NEEDLESS為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…迄今為止都那麼努力地闖關斬將殺到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把虛偽的勇氣掛在嘴邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什麼「努力終有回報」  「可能性不為零」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些自作多情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是弱者的自我暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力和祈禱  影響不了奇跡的發生率
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一隻螞蟻吵吵嚷嚷的  改變不了星球的運行軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球甚至不知道螞蟻它存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力和祈禱  影響不了奇跡發生的發生率  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你想的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什麼「怒了就能勝利」  「同伴死了就要贏」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些漂亮的奇跡根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對我來說  根本沒有依賴奇跡的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然與以往的敵人不可同日而語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  缺少本該擁有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你好了  ZERO的真正能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little boy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼巨大的little boy啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我這個原型的還要大好多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼他的招數會增強威力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是  積極反饋·ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積極反饋？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積極反饋就是  
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以核裂變為代表的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種反應被增幅促進  形成連鎖反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.51,0:17:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難理解啊  腦袋快要噴火了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經噴火咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的簡單一些的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是從互相吵架上升為打架鬥毆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼阿克萊特的積極反饋·ZERO是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  把所受的招數加強數倍再返給對方的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積極反饋這個能力  最終會趨向於大爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是最強的能力  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷德的能力  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把所受的招數原模原樣返給對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿克萊特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻能把任何攻擊加強之後再返給對方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠始終使用比對手厲害的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比它還強的能力  可以說是不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴旋引力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向天吐痰  就會返回給自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迴旋引力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不可能有勝算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與天作對  要悉數返還給自身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四波動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是單方蹂躪啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特這傢伙  又強了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是阿克萊特毫髮無損地活下來  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的安排可就亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個神父沒那麼弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還能看到曙光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體驗絕望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是失敗作與神的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然避開了我的要害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒察覺到嗎  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼自願讓你戳穿我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於有機會鑽進你的懷裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我奪來吧  把你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用額頭的白毫把阿克萊特的能力全都奪過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  才不是亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克萊特不敢三兩下就殺死佈雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  阿克萊特的目的是霸佔神父的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而心臟附近正是他最想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能扎穿心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引力子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好方法  一起封住了自己和阿克萊特的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不妨就打飛你脖子上面的部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引力子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  被抵消了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.73,0:21:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間在扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋裡有影像…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不是  逆排斥反應
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆排斥反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  和那時一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  那段令人忌恨的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恢復…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡啊  瑟肯多莉婭那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「左天大人  請您走樓梯」  啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說那部爛電梯  才能裝得下這點人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會有誰偷偷帶著很重的東西吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.05,0:23:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如金屬塊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.74,0:23:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的胳膊就是